Interface ResourcePath

  • All Known Implementing Classes:

      • getParent

        ResourcePath getParent()

      • getRoot

        ResourcePath getRoot()
        Returns:

      • getName

        String getName()
        Returns:
        the name of this ResourcePathNode as segment (this "folder" or "file").

      • isAbsolute

        boolean isAbsolute()
        Returns:
        true if this path is absolute, false if it is relative.

      • isRoot

        boolean isRoot()
        Returns:
        true if this is the root ResourcePathNode, false otherwise.
